2.00	Larry_Harris_(game_designer)	Larry Harris (game designer)	Larry Harris, Jr., is a game designer most famous for creating the board game Axis &amp; Allies, as well as all of its sequels. His other significant games include Conquest of the Empire, Broadsides and Boarding Parties, LionHeart and more. He has also assisted in the further development of Trivial Pursuit and Risk. Larry is also the inventor of Thin Ice.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Battle_Trebia-en.svg/150px-Battle_Trebia-en.svg.png
